'''飓风埃里克'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Erick}}）是[[2013年太平洋飓风季|2013年太平洋飓风季]]形成的第五个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]、第五场获命名的风暴和第四场飓风，于这年7月对墨西哥太平洋沿海地区构成轻微影响。系统源自6月18日离开非洲西海岸的[[东风波|东风波]]，在快速穿越大西洋期间基本没有发展，于7月1日进入东太平洋。由于外界环境有利，东风波于7月4日发展成热带低气压，再于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月5日凌晨0点进一步增强成热带风暴并获名“埃里克”。气旋总体朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向飘移，于7月6日成为[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|一级飓风]]，并在当天达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]130公里的最高强度。由于所在位置靠近陆地，行经海域水温也逐渐降低，埃里克的强度于次日回落到热带风暴标准，再在此强度下保持两天后于7月9日清晨退化成残留低气压区。数小时后，气旋的残留环流在[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]西南方向海域消散。

面对风暴来袭，墨西哥西海岸多地收到[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]。许多港口暂时封闭，官员建议生活在低洼地区的居民向地势更高的地点转移。此外，船运业务也暂时中止。虽然埃里克的中心始终位于海上没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，但其外围[[雨带|雨带]]在墨西哥西部部分地区产生强烈阵风和局部暴雨。[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]城市[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]和马尔克斯港发生轻度洪灾。[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]有一条河流泛滥，州内多个城市受到洪水影响，许多汽车、街道和民宅因此受损。一名女性在试图从被淹的家中逃离时不幸丧生，另有一名男子因被河水卷走而遇难。墨西哥军方和纳亚里特州政府救下数以百计的居民。风暴在南下加利福尼亚州大范围地区产生降水，引发洪灾。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Erick 2013 track.png}}
6月18日，有[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸进入东大西洋。系统接下来几天稳步西进，轴线周围保有规模偏小但组织严密的[[对流|对流]]区（即降雨和[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动）。6月24至29日，东风波先后穿越[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]和[[中美洲|中美洲]]，并在不久后进入东太平洋。<ref name="Etcr">{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Erick | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP052013_Erick.pdf | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 2013-08-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075354/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP052013_Erick.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-24 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>7月1日夜间，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始监控东风波，称其所在海域外界环境有利，预计系统会缓慢发展<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Todd B. Kimberlain | author2 = Stacy R. Stewart | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201307012335.txt | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075303/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201307012335.txt | accessdate = 2016-06-24 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。7月2日，东风波同大范围的[[低气压|低气压区]]相互影响，对流的覆盖范围因此扩大，还形成另一片大面积的低气压区。系统继续缓慢西进，在组织起足够的对流后于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月4日中午12点在中心位于墨西哥[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]东南方向约330公里洋面时成为热带低气压。<ref name="Etcr" />受中等强度[[风切变|风切变]]影响，气旋的环流中心起初暴露在外，但很快就因[[雨带|对流带]]范围加大并且渐趋弧形而增强<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Todd B. Kimberlain | author2 = Lixion A. Avila | title = Tropical Storm Erick Discussion Number 3 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-03 | accessdate = 2016-06-24 | location = Miami, Florida | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.003.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130846/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = no}}</ref>。面对这种情况，美国国家飓风中心于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}7月5日凌晨0点将气旋升级成热带风暴，并以“埃里克”（{{lang|en|Erick}}）命名<ref name="Etcr" />。

受西北[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]上空的中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]和[[美国西南部|美国西南部]]上空的上层高压脊影响，风暴获名后总体朝西北方向前进，移动路线同墨西哥西海岸基本平行<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack L. Beven | title = Tropical Storm Erick Discussion Number 4 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.004.shtml | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-05 | accessdate = 2016-06-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304141046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.004.shtml | deadurl = no | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。7月5日白天，气旋内形成[[中心密集云区|中心密集云区]]，卫星图像上可以看到紧密的对流带。此外，微波卫星图像表明还有[[风眼|风眼]]正在成型<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Eric S. Blake | author2 = Stacy R. Stewart | title = Tropical Storm Erick Discussion Number 6 | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002756/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.006.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.006.shtml | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-05 | accessdate = 2016-06-24 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。埃里卡的垂直结构起初存在相互分离的断层，但接下来逐渐变成紧密关联的整体。卫星图像上间歇出现形态还不规则的风眼，美国国家飓风中心于{{lang|en|UTC}}早上6点把位于墨西哥[[拉萨罗卡德纳斯|拉萨罗卡德纳斯]]西南偏西方向约170公里海域的风暴升级成一级飓风<ref name="Etcr" /><ref>{{cite report | author = Stacy R. Stewart | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063950/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.010.shtml | title = Hurricane Erick Discussion Number 10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.010.shtml | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-24 | location = Miami, Florida}}</ref>。结合卫星强度估算，气象部门估计气旋于{{lang|en|UTC}}中午12点达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时130公里，最低气压983[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.03[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。此后不久，埃里克开始因靠近墨西哥海岸且行经洋面[[海面温度|水温]]逐渐降低而减弱。<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | title = Hurricane Erick Discussion Number 11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205411/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.011.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.011.shtml | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-06 | accessdate = 2016-06-25 | location = Miami, Florida | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}7月7日下午18点，风暴关联对流已显著回暖，风眼也已消失，强度回落至热带风暴标准<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Eric S. Blake | author2 = Stacy R. Stewart | title = Tropical Storm Erick Discussion Number 13 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.013.shtml | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071150/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.013.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-25 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。7月9日，气旋从[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]以南近海经过，环流中心在风切变的影响下暴露出来<ref>{{cite report | author1 = David Zelinsky | author2 = James L. Franklin | title = Tropical Storm Erick Discussion Number 19 | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034639/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.019.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep05/ep052013.discus.019.shtml | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-08 | accessdate = 2016-06-25 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>，再于{{lang|en|UTC}}早上6点消退成残留低气压区。风暴残留接下来又持续存在数小时，最终于{{lang|en|UTC}}7月10日凌晨在水温偏低的海域上空逐渐消散。<ref name="Etcr" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Erick_2013-07-07_1805Z.jpg|thumb]]
宣布热带风暴埃里克成型的同时，气象机构向阿卡普尔科至拉福图纳（{{lang|en|La Fortuna}}）之间的墨西哥西南沿海地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]。到了{{lang|en|UTC}}7月5日凌晨3点，预警生效范围已从阿卡普尔科延伸至[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]，曼萨尼约至[[拉萨罗卡德纳斯|拉萨罗卡德纳斯]]又接获热带风暴警告。数小时后，阿卡普尔科至拉萨罗卡德纳斯间沿海地区的热带风暴观察预警取消，拉福图纳到哈利斯科州科连特斯角（{{lang|en|Cabo Corrientes}}）地区进入热带风暴观察预警生效状态。与此同时，拉萨罗卡德纳斯到曼萨尼约间的热带风暴警告也予中止，生效范围变更成拉福图纳至[[锡瓦塔内霍|锡瓦塔内霍]]。{{lang|en|UTC}}次日凌晨3点，所有热带风暴观察预警均停止生效，热带风暴警告的生效范围则从锡瓦塔内霍延伸至科连特斯角。埃里克升级成飓风后，气象部门向蓬塔圣特尔莫到科连特斯角发布飓风观察预警。{{lang|en|UTC}}7月6日下午15点，圣菲（{{lang|en|Santa Fe}}）到[[拉巴斯_(南下加利福尼亚州)|拉巴斯]]收到热带风暴观察预警，并在数小时后升级成热带风暴警告。经过多次升、降级和生效范围变更，所有热带气旋警告最终在7月9日清晨埃里克退化成残留低气压区后中止。<ref name="Etcr" />

面对风暴威胁，[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]南部、[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]南部和[[科利马州|科利马州]]收到“橙色”警告，哈利斯科州其它沿海地区则是“黄色”警告<ref name="EEU6">{{cite news | title = Alertan por llegada de huracán Erick a Jaliso | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131104060624/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/huracan-erick-jalisco-934272.html | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/huracan-erick-jalisco-934272.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-07-06 | archivedate = 2013-11-04 | accessdate = 2013-11-04 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。位于阿卡普尔科、锡瓦塔内霍和曼萨尼约的港口关闭<ref name="EEU1" />。由于担心爆发山洪，政府官员敦促生活在阿卡普尔科低洼地区的居民撤离<ref name="Erick 13">{{cite news | title = La tormenta tropical Erick pone en alerta al pacifico mexicano | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065645/http://mexico.cnn.com/nacional/2013/07/05/la-tormenta-tropical-erick-pone-en-alerta-al-pacifico-mexicano | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | newspaper = CNN Mexico | date = 2013-07-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://expansion.mx/nacional/2013/07/05/la-tormenta-tropical-erick-pone-en-alerta-al-pacifico-mexicano | archivedate = 2016-03-04}}</ref>。与此同时，米却肯州政府下令船只断航<ref name="EEU3">{{cite news | title = Suspenden navegación en Michoacán por Erick | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/michoacan-tormenta-erick--934138.html | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-12-18 | archivedate = 2013-12-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131219041130/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/michoacan-tormenta-erick--934138.html | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

埃里克的中心自始至终位于海上，但其外围[[雨带|雨带]]还是在墨西哥西南沿海地区产生暴雨和强烈阵风<ref name="EEU1">{{cite news | title = Autoridades de Acapulco, en alerta por tormenta Erick | archivedate = 2013-11-03 | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/autoridades-de-acapulco-en-alerta-por-tormenta-erick-934008.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131103085613/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/autoridades-de-acapulco-en-alerta-por-tormenta-erick-934008.html | accessdate = 2013-11-03 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-07-05 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，并且影响范围还在朝西北方向延伸<ref name="Erick13">{{cite news | title = México seguirá afectado por lluvias | url = http://noticierostelevisa.esmas.com/clima/617154/mexico-seguira-afectado-lluvias/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095259/http://noticierostelevisa.esmas.com/clima/617154/mexico-seguira-afectado-lluvias/ | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | newspaper = Noticierosa Televisa | date = 2013-07-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。风暴导致阿卡普尔科和马尔克斯港发生轻度洪灾<ref name="EEU2">{{cite news | author = Adriana Covarrubias | title = Acapulco y Zihuatanejo cierran bahías por Erick | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-07-05 | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/erick-tormenta-guerrero-acapulco-zihuatanejo-934135.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131219040747/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/erick-tormenta-guerrero-acapulco-zihuatanejo-934135.html | archivedate = 2013-12-19 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2013-12-19}}</ref>，格雷罗州其它地区所受破坏程度很轻，大部分是因[[山崩|山体滑坡]]引起<ref name="EM">{{cite news | title = "Erick"deja inundaciones en Guerrero | accessdate = 2016-07-01 | newspaper = El Mexicano | date = 2013-07-06 | archivedate = 2013-07-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130708150958/http://www.el-mexicano.com.mx/informacion/noticias/1/2/nacional/2013/07/05/681804/erickdeja-inundaciones-en-guerrero | deadurl = no | url = http://www.el-mexicano.com.mx/informacion/noticias/1/2/nacional/2013/07/05/681804/erickdeja-inundaciones-en-guerrero}}</ref>。科利马州沿海地区测得2.7米的大浪<ref name="EEU5">{{cite news | title = Amenaza Erick costa de Colima; registran marejadas | accessdate = 2013-11-03 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-07-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131103085944/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/amenaza-erick-costa-de-colima-registran-marejadas-934275.html | archivedate = 2013-11-03 | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/amenaza-erick-costa-de-colima-registran-marejadas-934275.html}}</ref>，该州虽有部分地区发生洪灾，但总体破坏程度很轻<ref name="EEF">{{cite news | last = Jiménez Padilla | first = Jesús | title = Huracán Erick provoca inundaciones en Nayarit; en Colima cierran puerto | archivedate = 2013-12-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131219064550/http://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/component/content/article/47/21850.html | url = http://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/component/content/article/47/21850.html | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | newspaper = El Financiero | date = 2013-07-07}}</ref>。

气旋在更北面的[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]引发大范围洪灾<ref name="NC">{{cite news | title = Huracán Erick causa muerte e inundación en Nayarit | url = https://noticabos.org/2013/07/07/huracan-erick-causa-muerte-e-inundacion-en-nayarit/ | accessdate = 2016-07-02 | newspaper = Noti Cabos | date = 2013-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-03-23 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160323021525/http://noticabos.org/2013/07/07/huracan-erick-causa-muerte-e-inundacion-en-nayarit/ }}</ref>。一名74岁的老妇人在试图逃离被淹的房屋时遇难，另有数十辆汽车受损，多条街道和多户民居被淹。该州一条河流泛滥成灾，多个城市受到影响。州内官员设法营救数以百计受到飓风影响的灾民，<ref name="NC" />许多人都在街上等待救援<ref name="Erick">{{cite news | title = Huracán Erick provoca inundaciones en Nayarit; en Colima cierran puerto | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | newspaper = Nototica | date = 2013-07-07 | archivedate = 2013-12-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131219064555/http://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/component/content/article/47-politicasociedad/21850-huracan-erick-provoca-inundaciones-en-nayarit-en-colima-cierran-puerto.html | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/component/content/article/47-politicasociedad/21850-huracan-erick-provoca-inundaciones-en-nayarit-en-colima-cierran-puerto.html}}</ref>。数十户家庭直接受到风暴影响，街道上有大量瓦砾堆积。当地居民遭受重大经济损失，并以艾克萨里斯科（{{lang|en|Xalisco}}）情况严重，需宣告为灾区。该州近海还出现[[海龙卷风|海龙卷风]]。<ref name="EEF" />州长罗伯托·桑多瓦尔（{{lang|en|Roberto Sandoval}}）宣布[[特皮克|特皮克]]进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="Erick" />。虽然埃里克的核心自始至终位于海上没有登陆，但[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]还是进入“黄色”预警状态。下加利福尼亚半岛普降暴雨，引发洪灾。拉巴斯、[[卡波圣卢卡斯|卡波圣卢卡斯]]（{{lang|en|Cabo San Lucas}}）和[[圣荷西卡波|圣荷西卡波]]（{{lang|en|San Jose del Cabo}}）港因海浪高涨关闭。<ref>{{cite news | title = BCS cierra puertos por tormenta tropical Erick | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131219040744/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/tormenta-tropical-erick-lluvias-bcs-alerta-934645.html | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-07-08 | archivedate = 2013-12-19 | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/tormenta-tropical-erick-lluvias-bcs-alerta-934645.html}}</ref>此外，下加利福尼亚州还收到“绿色”预警<ref>{{cite news | title = Erick se acerca a península de Baja California | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/tormenta-erick-baja-california-934641.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131219040435/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/2013/tormenta-erick-baja-california-934641.html | accessdate = 2013-12-19 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-07-08 | archivedate = 2013-12-19}}</ref>。整场风暴共造成两人丧生，另有两人失踪<ref name="AFP">{{cite news | title = Tropical storm Erick leaves two dead and two missing in Mexico | accessdate = 2016-07-04 | date = 2013-07-09 | agency = [[法新社|Agence France-Presse]] | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rawstory.com/2013/07/tropical-storm-erick-leaves-two-dead-and-two-missing-in-mexico/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160405194738/http://www.rawstory.com/2013/07/tropical-storm-erick-leaves-two-dead-and-two-missing-in-mexico/ | archivedate = 2016-04-05}}</ref>。艾克萨里斯科约有5500人无家可归<ref name="Erick 07">{{cite news | title = Mexican hurricane Erick leaves 1 dead, 3 missing | accessdate = 2016-07-04 | newspaper = Before its news | url = http://beforeitsnews.com/weather/2013/07/mexican-hurricane-erick-leaves-1-dead-3-missing-2441134.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304025945/http://beforeitsnews.com/weather/2013/07/mexican-hurricane-erick-leaves-1-dead-3-missing-2441134.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | date = 2013-07-09}}</ref>。

